msContents.summary: Poetic and mythological sayings and maxims compiled as a repository of ethical and political guidance and instructions for making good decisions through poetry and Hindu mythology. Manuscript is comprised of the second and largest of four sections (skandha) that make up this work. There is a table of contents at the beginning of the manuscript (f. i-iv).
